platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: 快眠と不安解消の瞑想

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: As its name suggests, Insight Timer started as a simple timer app for meditating. But it’s evolved into a comprehensive (and award-winning) way to help people reduce anxiety, improve their sleep, and maybe even gain a little insight along the way. It features thousands of guided meditations across a range of styles: Buddhist mindfulness (which channels your inner monk), Kundalini yoga (which focuses on your posture), walking meditation (which is meditation on the move), and many others. Lessons range from just a few minutes to long and luxurious.

This app started as a simple timer app for meditating, but it’s evolved into a comprehensive way to help people, while gaining insight along the way. With lessons which range from short to long and luxurious, it features thousands of guided meditations across a range of styles.
瞑想のためのシンプルなタイマーが、その過程で洞察を得られる、人々を総合的にサポートするアプリに進化しました。短いものや長いもの、豪華なものなど数多くのレッスンが用意され、様々なスタイルのガイド付き瞑想を数千種類も楽しめます。

Cette app a commencé comme un simple minuteur pour vous aider à méditer, mais elle a évolué en un outil complet de bien-être. Avec des leçons courtes ou plus longues, elle propose des milliers de méditations guidées en tous genres.
這個 App 最初是純粹的冥想計時 App，但現已發展出更多功能，令你在得到助益的同時更了解自己。課程有長有短，內容豐富，提供數千種不同風格的冥想指導。
這款 App 最初是簡單的冥想計時器，如今已發展成全方位的身心靈成長平台。它提供從短期到深度的課程，並擁有數千種不同風格的引導式冥想。
